<td class="navbox-group" style=";;">Modern cartridges used</td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><a href="/wiki/5.56x45mm_NATO" title="5.56x45mm NATO">5.56x45mm NATO (.223 Remington)</a> • <a href="/wiki/7.62x51_NATO" title="7.62x51 NATO" class="mw-redirect">7.62x51mm NATO (.308 Win)</a> • <a href="/wiki/.50_BMG" title=".50 BMG">12.7x99mm NATO (.50 BMG)</a> • <a href="/wiki/.338_Lapua" title=".338 Lapua" class="mw-redirect">.338 Lapua</a> • <a href="/wiki/9x19mm_Parabellum" title="9x19mm Parabellum">9x19mm Parabellum</a> • <a href="/wiki/12_gauge" title="12 gauge" class="mw-redirect">12 gauge</a></div>
